<br>
&quot;And we get a U.N. resolution passed that says we can go after folks who go offshore with nuclear weapons activity and do a cleanup operation when it comes to people transiting and materials transiting and the like,&quot; Sokolski says. &quot;No war. You'll notice, no war.&quot; <br>
<br>
